b'{"data_headers":{"result_code":1},"data":{"information":{"article_id":639,"category_name":"News","pr_category_id":"1","title_name":"Issue Regarding Afflictions[Addendum]","message":"<div>We have confirmed an issue in version 1.10.0 where certain afflictions do not take effect properly despite the visual effects of the affliction appearing.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>We are currently investigating this issue.<\/div><div>Any updates will be added to this notice.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div><span style=\\"color: rgb(44, 130, 201);\\"><strong>[Addendum <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1564404300\\"><\/span>]<\/strong><\/span><\/div><div>As a temporary measure, we will be reverting the affliction mechanic back to that of 1.9.1 in the next data update scheduled to take place at <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1564462800\\"><\/span>.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Also, changes to afflictions will be postponed to a later update in order to fix this issue in version 1.10.0.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div><span style=\\"color: rgb(44, 130, 201);\\"><strong>[Addendum <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1564478400\\"><\/span>]<\/strong><\/span><\/div><div>We have reverted the affliction mechanic back to that of version 1.9.1 in the data update applied at <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1564462800\\"><\/span> before the automatic update.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>We will announce the agenda for the affliction mechanic changes that were originally planned in version 1.10.0 in a separate notice.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div><span style=\\"color: rgb(44, 130, 201);\\"><strong>[Addendum <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1567058400\\"><\/span>]<br><\/strong><\/span>The changes to how afflictions work, which were scheduled for release in version 1.10.0, were applied in an automatic update performed around <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1567047600\\"><\/span>.<br><br>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.<\/div>","start_time":1564387200,"prev_article_id":"640","next_article_id":"643","image_path":"","update_time":1567058560}}}'